        CR
        CR ." ? " TYPE  HONK
        SOURCE-ID @ 0>  ( source is NOT console)
        IF  ."  Line " LINES @ DECIMAL U.
            CR CR SOURCE TYPE
        THEN ABORT
      THEN 2DROP ;

